description	"Remnant Swamptrooper - Rocketeer

^2Weaponry:
- SE-14R Light Repeating Pistol (2)
- Merr Sonn PLX-2M Missile System (15 Rockets)
- 3 Trip Mines
- 2 Pulse Grenade

^8Attributes:
- Blast Armour
- Stamina (2)
- Reinforcements (1)
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]

An imperial Remnant Swamptrooper armed with a portable Rocket launcher. This swamptrooper has thicker armor to withstand explosive blasts, but is slower as a result. It carries a grapple hook to assist it with mobility to gaining a tactical advantage from the high ground."